    In a school race , Tula run 2.45 km‚Äîthat is 2 full kilometers, 400 meters (4 tenths of a km), and 50 meters (5 hundredths of a km). 
    We use total value of digits in a decimal to identify the distance Talu ran that could not form a whole number.
  </p>
